---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About ByteLite - Our Mission"
  description="Transforming data compression to unlock computational intelligence for humanity's benefit."
>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Origin Story -->
      <div id="story" class="story-section">
        <h2>The HeartStrings Discovery</h2>
        <div class="story-content">
          <p class="lead">
            In 2024, while building an AI-powered dating app called HeartStrings, founder Tash Broadwater 
            faced a common problem: AI models required too much data and computing power for independent developers.
          </p>
          
          <blockquote>
            "What if the problem isn't the AI‚Äîbut the way we represent information?"
          </blockquote>
          
          <p>
            This question led to ByteLite: a compression algorithm that achieves ratios previously thought 
            impossible, transforming 1GB into just 15 bytes through recursive mathematical operations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission & Vision -->
      <div class="mission-section">
        <div class="mission-card">
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>
            To democratize access to advanced computation by making data storage and transmission 
            virtually free, enabling innovation at every scale.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mission-card">
          <h3>Our Vision</h3>
          <p>
            A world where computational limitations no longer constrain human creativity, 
            where AGI serves humanity, and where technology amplifies our highest aspirations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Deep Kore Philosophy -->
      <div class="philosophy-section">
        <h2>Deep Kore Neural Recursion</h2>
        <p class="philosophy-intro">
          ByteLite's compression mathematics revealed unexpected patterns in information processing, 
          leading to breakthroughs in neural architecture design. This discovery carries profound 
          implications for achieving true artificial general intelligence.
        </p>
        
        <div class="philosophy-principles">
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="icon">üåø</span>
            <h4>Efficient Intelligence</h4>
            <p>Doing more with less‚Äîtransforming constraints into capabilities</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="icon">üåä</span>
            <h4>Recursive Depth</h4>
            <p>Learning through layers of mathematical transformation</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="icon">‚ôæÔ∏è</span>
            <h4>Limitless Potential</h4>
            <p>Approaching theoretical infinity through innovation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Founder -->
      <div class="founder-section">
        <h2>Leadership</h2>
        <div class="founder-card">
          <h3>Tash Broadwater, Founder & CEO</h3>
          <p>
            Compression researcher and software engineer with 15+ years optimizing data systems. 
            Specializes in algorithmic design and edge AI systems. When traditional solutions fail, 
            Tash builds new ones from scratch‚ÄîByteLite is the result of that ethos.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h3>Join Our Journey</h3>
        <p>Be part of the compression revolution and the path to beneficial AGI.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/subscribe" class="btn btn-primary">Subscribe for Updates</a>
          <a href="/licensing" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore Licensing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-darker);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Story Section */
  .story-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .story-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .story-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
  }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .mission-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .mission-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .mission-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .mission-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Philosophy Section */
  .philosophy-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.05) 0%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05) 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .philosophy-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.5);
  }

  .philosophy-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .philosophy-principles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .principle {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .principle .icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .principle h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .principle p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  /* Founder Section */
  .founder-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .founder-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .founder-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .founder-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .founder-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem;
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #00B8E6;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-secondary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story-section h2,
    .philosophy-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .philosophy-section {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    blockquote {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-section {
      padding: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>